snippet: Quarterback Tom Brady led four scoring drives -- two after turnovers -- and New England's defense kept the Denver Broncos out of the end zone Sunday in a 16-3 victory that clinched the Patriots' eighth straight AFC East title and the playoff berth...
lead_paragraph: Quarterback Tom Brady led four scoring drives -- two after turnovers -- and New England's defense kept the Denver Broncos out of the end zone Sunday in a 16-3 victory that clinched the Patriots' eighth straight AFC East title and the playoff berth that goes with it.

headline.main: Patriots Beat Broncos, Clinch NFL-Record Eighth Division Title
headline.print_headline: Patriots Beat Broncos, Clinch NFL-Record Eighth Division Title
